{"tid":2233574,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"隱身之葉 - 古德明","createTime":"2020-10-07T08:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T08:36:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0f01e2503d25d8bd735aabf651f071742df0ab90","tid":2233574,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T08:36:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201007/WALCLN7IGNBZ7DMAN7MRWAKBVY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201007%2FWALCLN7IGNBZ7DMAN7MRWAKBVY%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=b77b16d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201007%2FWALCLN7IGNBZ7DMAN7MRWAKBVY%2F&h=fa5ea47e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201007/WALCLN7IGNBZ7DMAN7MRWAKBVY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隱身之葉 - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TxPuyX1PTFsSXFpQn21gRF4kmpU=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PLJNT3DGFZFDRGTT3KMGBAB2IY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTxPuyX1PTFsSXFpQn21gRF4kmpU%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPLJNT3DGFZFDRGTT3KMGBAB2IY.png&h=45f3ef15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有線電視新聞部最近大整肅，多位要員去職，迎來無綫電視新聞部前副總監許方輝，主掌新聞編務方針。他甫上任就聲明：「我並無政治任務。」按無綫新聞部向來以「官方喉舌」見稱，許方輝之聲明未免多餘。<br />\n<br />\n一九九七年七月之前，香港總督施政，教育以至傳播機關等任免大員，從沒聽過要附加「並無政治因素」的注腳。今日可不同了，幾乎事事都鄭重聲明「並無政治因素」。例如新香港長官鄭月娥五月二十五日發表《抗疫四月》一文，特別申言：「或謂政府禁群眾聚集，有政治因素，這是毫無根據的。」七月三十一日，她頒令禁止立法會改選，又特別申言：「這是個艱難的決定，純粹為了防疫，沒有政治因素。」港共元老曾鈺成都忍不住說：「當然沒有人相信啦，哈哈哈！」<br />\n<br />\n三國時代魏國邯鄲淳《笑林》載：。。。。。。。。。。。。。。縛送官。<br />\n<br />\n那片隱身之葉，今日猶存，名曰「並無政治因素」；而楚國那貧士，今日則變做達官貴人了。"}]}